reviewText: My daughter loves the movies. I received them in great time box wasn't damaged. All DVDs played great.
I love all of these movies, so much. The shipping was ridiculously fast. And to top it all off, each of the movies came in its own case. So it's like paying only $2 for each movie.
Love the full screen, I wish that they still made ALL movies in full screen.
came in the mail at a fast rate, item in great condition, DVD's work great. overall, really happy with this purchase! quality childhood movies i missed for a small amount of money!

If I didn't already own all 3 of these movies on DVD, I would buy this DVD set.  I love all the movies included and it's a great price for 3 movies.  Since I don't have this particular pack, I don't know if it has special features on it or if it's just the movie, but if the movies all have the same special features, this would be an amazing pick!
They are cute teenage girl movies.  Even though Im not a teenager I still enjoyed them a lot.  All three movies are recommended,
